{"id":166065,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201177/","date":"2011-07-08T06:00:23Z","modified":"2011-07-08T06:00:23Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/7/7","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18929238?story_id=18929238&#038;fsrc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">香港人的抗议反映出不满的风潮</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——今年香港的七一游行是近年来中国境内最大规模的抗议活动。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110707/wl_nm/us_china_usa_dalailama\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国警告美国官员不要与达赖喇嘛见面</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国负责全球事务的副国务卿和众议院两党领袖都已和他见了面</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110707/wl_asia_afp/chinaunrestcharges\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国官方媒体称增城官员被开除，</span>11<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人因骚乱被起诉</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——六月发生骚乱的增城市，市长和党委书记都被开除</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/07/07/why-china-is-trying-to-censor-talk-about-jiang-zemin/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么中国要封杀关于江泽民的议论？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——因为共产党明白，前领导人的去世有可能会引发政治不稳定，比如</span><span>76</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年和</span><span>89</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>CNN:<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/07/07/china.jiang.zemin.health/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国官方媒体：江泽民逝世“纯属谣言”</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新华社出面辟谣。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/scene/2011/07/07/a-chinese-dissidents-literary-roll-call/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国异议作家马建点评五位作家</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“我觉得卡夫卡好像还活着。在中国，我能感到他无处不在”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国家利益：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nationalinterest.org/commentary/china-trounce-us-next-decade-5573\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在未来十年将大胜美国</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于中国主导的世界，西方不应感到害怕，而是应该理解并欢迎。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://lawprofessors.typepad.com/china_law_prof_blog/2011/07/who-owns-the-chinese-internet.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">谁控制着中国的互联网？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中央党校的学者认为外国资本控制着互联网，然而事实表明是党在控制互联网</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/chinas-economy-hits-first-hard-wall-205427240.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济撞上了第一道墙</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的房地产业和美国一样，是金融业和政治的延续。在房地产问题上，中国领导人现在处在膨胀或是萎缩的两难境地。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商业内幕：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/china-economy-hard-landing-bumpy-landing-soft-landing-and-what-landing-2011-7?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济的硬着陆、软着陆与不着陆</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然中国政府年初的时候计划采取紧缩政策，但现在看来他们已陷入两难。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2011/07/06/chinas-debt-monster?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">辩论室：中国的债务问题</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——七位经济学家就中国的地方债务问题展开讨论</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/07/business/global/building-binge-by-chinas-cities-threatens-countrys-economic-boom.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss&#038;pagewanted=all\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的建设热潮引发对债务超载的担忧</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的国家资本主义比外表看来的样子要混乱，经济也比外表看来的要脆弱</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/blog/2011/jul/07/china-oil-spill-cover-up-bohai-sea\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国石油泄露面积堪比半个伦敦，被掩盖了一个月才曝光</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——污染的海水，含混的信息，愤怒的公众。这一切都似曾相识。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/07/06/cover-up-culture-chinas-hidden-oil-spill-2/#axzz1RNHWTT1A\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“捂盖子”文化：中国的石油泄漏暴露出的问题</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在一个不透明、不公开的环境中，工业事故和环境灾难如何处理？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁金斯研究所：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.brookings.edu/speeches/2011/0520_china_bush.aspx?rssid=china&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+BrookingsRSS%2Ftopics%2Fchina+%28Brookings%3A+Topics+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“中华民国”在两岸关系中的重要性</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管北京认为“中华民国”在</span><span>49</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年之后就不存在了，但它至今仍占据着两岸争执的核心</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交关系委员会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cfr.org/east-asia/cross-strait-cooperation-fighting-crime/p25434?cid=rss-asia-cross_strait_cooperation_in_fi-070611&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+region%2Fasia+%28CFR.org+-+Regions+-+Asia%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">跨海峡合作打击犯罪</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——海峡两岸的法院和检查院开展合作，共同打击犯罪现象</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/07/07/china-and-the-philippines/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国与菲律宾</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——继越南之后，菲律宾也表示愿意就南海问题和中国进行谈判。“我们对中国的挑衅不满，但我们打不过中国。”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基国际和平基金会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=44968&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南中国海：所有各方的危险</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在下周召开的东盟区域论坛上，南海问题将成为各方的争论焦点</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/07/business/global/building-binge-by-chinas-cities-threatens-countrys-economic-boom.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss&#038;pagewanted=all\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲的多边团体是否失去了目标？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——亚洲大量的多边国际组织互有重叠，功能不清，使得其目的和效率都打了折扣</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jzSgZdSL9zALMf8U71IcO6raI5Ng?docId=CNG.9490a3c93c5695a77a8896bf0f174463.131\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">瑞典教育部长表示十年内在全部小学中开始汉语课</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他认为这对提升瑞典竞争力很重要</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>BetaNews</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.betanews.com/joewilcox/article/Did-Google-hand-China-to-Microsoft/1309920993\">Google<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">是否把中国拱手交给了微软？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——如果不是</span><span>Google</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在十八个月前勇敢地退出了中国，百度和微软最近达成的协议几乎毫无可能</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社独家报道：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110707/bs_nm/us_china_industries\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国可能会削减对关键行业的投资</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——出于对腐败和产能过剩的担心，北京将减少对高铁和风能产业的投入。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国金融市场：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mpettis.com/2011/07/incentives-and-debt/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">奖励与债务</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——国有企业的“多样化”经营使得大量资金进入房地产行业，从而将债务水平提升到了不可持续的程度</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bittman.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/07/06/chinas-bizarre-food-safety-scene-and-our-own/?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国形形色色的食品安全问题</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然中国的食品安全触目惊心，但美国的情况也没好到哪里去</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/07/06/red_chinas_green_buildings\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】红色中国的绿色建筑</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/07/06/the_green_leap_forward\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">绿色大跃进</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——从理论上，中国有机会避免西方在环境问题上的覆辙。但全面更改建筑规范，以推广绿色建筑的任务十分艰巨</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/07/07/but-its-not-my-fault-family-and-face-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">这不是我的错</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的家庭和面子</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：您可以到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>看到推友们对该篇译文的评论和转发；欢迎参与！如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-1932218719387878907?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":451,"categories":[1],"tags":[8840,13471]}